{"tid":2242290,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"笑死 大家係咪唔記得Apple點樣害我地？","createTime":"2020-10-14T02:21:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-14T08:58:51.000Z","uid":69221,"like":31,"dislike":59,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"8839136a3f0deb3411456d4d9a3b199a5ee367e4","tid":2242290,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T02:21:34.000Z","msg":"蘋果道咗歉未？<br />\n你地成班對唔對得住抗爭者？<br />\n<br />\n一開始講到天琦走得太前，又話要光復香港，又話多謝勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成撚日暗串香港人善忘 事實上最撚善忘係你班連登仔 屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n黎智英:港獨係鬼<br />\n武漢琦係鬼，搞港獨俾位中共入<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4iknu89.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4iknu89.jpg&h=2acbbeb9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2h5R7VP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2h5R7VP.png&h=44724266&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9PBU5Hv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9PBU5Hv.png&h=7037183e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tv5uUBk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftv5uUBk.png&h=e0d64604&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n扯口罩影勇武大頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蘋果紅撚到咁都買 你地係咪人？咁都原諒得 唔爭在原諒埋吉野家啦屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講一套做一套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad188e02211db83a26c11626f7a9150ab418fee9","tid":2242290,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T02:23:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5db872daef3ebb35af03cc5dfeb47eb454b1837e","tid":2242290,"uid":181502,"like":19,"dislike":3,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T02:24:12.000Z","msg":"我同樓主轉睇文匯報好耐了<img src=\"/assets/fa